  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities/#TOC-Energy-Immunity-and-Vulnerability\">&nbsp;fire resistance</a>&nbsp;10. At 5th level, when in contact with flame or a burning object (including a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons/magic-weapon-special-abilities/flaming/\">flaming</a>&nbsp;weapon, lantern, or torch), add 1 per die to any healing effect of which you are the target. At 9th level, your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities/#TOC-Energy-Immunity-and-Vulnerability\">fire resistance</a>&nbsp;increases to 20. At 20th level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities/#TOC-Energy-Immunity-and-Vulnerability\">immunity</a>&nbsp;to fire.</p>"
